anges (fine lines). (a) Overall (<italic>n</italic>&#x000a0;=&#x000a0;12). (b) Basal&#x02013;bolus treatment (<italic>n</italic>&#x000a0;=&#x000a0;6). (c) Basal (basal insulin only; <italic>n</italic>&#x000a0;=&#x000a0;6). (d) Insulin degludec. <styled-content style="fixed-case">TCS</styled-content>, total colonoscopy.</p></caption><graphic id="nlm-graphic-3" xlink:href="JDI-7-374-g001"/></fig><table-wrap id="jdi12409-tbl-0002" xml:lang="en" orientation="portrait" position="float"><label>Table 2</label><caption><p>Parameters of glucose variability in patients treated with insulin degludec during the daytime control period and daytime fasting period</p></caption><table frame="hsides" rules="groups"><col style="border-right:solid 1px #000000" span="1"/><col style="border-right:solid 1px #000000" span="1"/><col style="border-right:solid 1px #000000" span="1"/><col style="border-right:solid 1px #000000" span="1"/><col style="border-right:solid 1px #000000" span="1"/><col style="border-right:solid 1px #000000" span="1"/><col style="border-right:solid 1px #000000" span="1"/><col style="border-right:solid 1px #000000" span="1"/><col style="border-right:solid 1px #000000" span="1"/><col style="border-right:solid 1px #000000" span="1"/><thead valign="top"><tr style="border-bottom:solid 1px #000000"><th align="left" rowspan="2" valign="top" colspan="1"/><th align="left" colspan="2" style="border-bottom:solid 1px #000000" valign="top" rowspan="1">Overall</th><th align="left" rowspan="2" valign="top" colspan="1">
